<%- include("header") -%>
<div class="header-spacer"></div>

<div class="container contact-container">
  <h1 class="page-header">Contact</h1>

  <p class="page-top-text">
    Have a question, comment or concern? Please dont hesitate to reach out. For most inquiries you can
    email us at <a href="mailto: ece@skule.ca">ece@skule.ca</a>, to reach out to a particular club member, you can find all of our emails in the about us page.
    Finally, if you would like to send us an anonymous message you can use the form below.
  </p>

  <form action="https://ececlubemail.herokuapp.com/sendemail" method="post">
    <div class="form-group">
      <label for="title-text-area">Title</label>
      <input type="text" class="form-control" id="title-text-area" name="title">
    </div>

    <div class="form-group">
      <label for="body-text-area">Message</label>
      <textarea class="form-control rounded-0" id="body-text-area" rows="10" name="body"></textarea>
    </div>
    <button class="btn btn-secondary" type="submit" name="button">Submit Anonymous Feedback</button>
    <p class="mt-2">It could take up to 30 seconds to send your email, so if your browser keeps refreshing, please be patient, you will be sent to a success page.</p>
  </form>


</div>

<div class="footer-spacer"></div>
<%- include("footer") -%>
